[As the cases increase, a 3rd mold _Cladosporium_ has been isolated from one case and the strain of _Exserohilum_ isolated from clinical cases seems, not surprisingly to be the same as the strain isolated from the implicated vehicle.

The 3rd posting is the 1st report of a clinical case, illustrating how aggressive the infection may be. There may be a great deal of difference in the amount of inoculum in different patients which can reflect the differences in clinical features and if the infection becomes manifest at all.

Related to the date of reporting (not date of onset), the number of cases, number of states involved, and deaths are:

